name: Christmas 2021
description:
This is a Christmas gift to my collectors and supporters in my first 4 months in the Tezos space. Thank you for your kindness and welcoming culture! May all of you have a relaxing yet cheerful time with your loved ones and find piece during the next days.

It shows the Lukas church in Wiesbaden, Germany, by architect Fritz Soeder. Recommended to be viewed in 1:1 scale, although it adapts to screen size after refresh.
